itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 7/29.

Turns out Rosenberg might've been right about Starships (32:00) !!!! Ebro and the crew give away Summer Jam tickets, Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments (17, & 1:06), and the Gurus help you out (59). Can we end robocalls? (46)
